Tool

Class Game

  • java.lang.Object
    • Tool.Game

  • public class Game
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains all the information to make a Gueser find a city in a game against the computer. The clues are a list of prerecorded clues from human vs human games. The different methods of this class allow to manage the clues and the solution related to one city guess.
    Author:
    kemoadrian
